  <brief_title>506U78 In Relapsed Or Refractory Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia (T-ALL)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II-Study With Nelarabine in Patients With Refractory Oder Relapsed T- ALL or T-lymphoblastic Lymphoma (Amend.7)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
